Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與來自神秘遠方的敵人 － {\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei} 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此毫無妥協的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一些人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一個講述無休止的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.26,pic1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(551,425)\frz-20}（歡慶畢業）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉行了那一年的第二個「畢業」典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…今與諸位學長分別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人深感惆悵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們絕不會忘記諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請學長們一切珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿忘島上渡過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祝願身體健康 工作順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹表贈別之意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭賀諸位畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有學生會長氣勢的告別辭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 副會長幫我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你這懶蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和你分別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空會回來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「畢業」成了定局之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有些不適應 對這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘快融入大人之中反而更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早點確定自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁還能活在義務教育世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如向喜歡的人告白之類的 什麼都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心存遺憾是最糟糕的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有留下遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,義務教育都沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就進入完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是龍宮島特有的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和劍司一如既往的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還賭劍司贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士賭哪邊贏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提劍司是13連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去可是很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和總士 他們倆小時候常在一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在一起玩是有原因的吧 相互之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要低頭懇求身為副會長的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我養著牠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！帶牠一起走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 藏前 接下來的事拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長竟然先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道明天有休學典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想說是去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他能撐著來就已經很辛苦了 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 那傢伙是個懶蟲也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們加油幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 只是有些貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你還挺熱心腸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看你表情很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎沒跟其他人一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別老等著劍司那樣的人衝到面前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要主動和別人搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說你幫了我 說這話好像不大厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去遠見醫生那邊喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間也來作檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡覺之前還好好的 今天卻不能上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是遺傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長得的病跟媽媽一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然和媽媽沒有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很羡慕羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有位真心體貼你的好母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,減少止疼藥的劑量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 無法再復原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀也有可能完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說那個選拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 情況一定不會悲觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 聽說可以自願參加 鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最害怕一事無成就結束了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親去世已經兩年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨立生活有困難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島這麼小 總有人幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 我也不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間 不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 有個好朋友真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的好朋友一半以上都「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持上學 還當學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我休假時 大家擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 一上學就突然多了個頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這樣 不覺得討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像硬塞給你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒有忘記我 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為我準備了容身之處 我應該報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算去學校 恐怕也沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜陪在你身邊的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長 真壁叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我馬上去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 只是來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心養病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天上午又舉行「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放暑假之前 舉行好幾次「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡是個荒僻的小島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸小時候的畢業典禮也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我「畢業」後會去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会陪在爸爸身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连带妈妈的份一直陪在您身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門重複發出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計700小時之內將得到明確應答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不能迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的核正在形成人格 若此時和敵人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整座島都被奪取的可能性太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是只能將防禦系統降低到極限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們直接跟生駒談了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點將全部{\fnArial}Fafner{\r}相關兵器嚴密封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為將被敵人奪取後的打擊降到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能主動封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 僅此實在不能算是萬全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對此生駒所提出迴避危機的計劃 即是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若要實施 {\fnArial}TSX{\fnsimhei}的投入是大前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 難道要讓孩子們參與嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要掌控這個島的人們共同決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（暑假）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要打贏你 別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未前辈是学生会副会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会觉得很辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要面对在学校里带着狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还工作偷懒的学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能觉得很有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副会长的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是学生会长他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢……两方都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天要和朋友出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友約我去海邊玩 很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒讓我想起這島雖小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候卻也不愁找不到地方玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你約我來的 自己卻不下去游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的泳姿 就失去信心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你去看過遠見醫生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微能明白這樣的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直和爸爸生活在一起 習慣照顧人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體也曬暖了 去游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒想過讓別人照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果傷了你的心 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很開心 許久未曾這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能稍微拋開爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Al…vis…{\fnsimhei}必須…得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去{\fnArial}Alvis…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士同學 令尊常去看我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 說是在公事上聽取一些建議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Plan…L
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner…Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嗎 你在那裡嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,識別限制編碼確認為第三級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TS…X
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀你「畢業」 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音一直在我腦海裡迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習({\fnArial}Memorizing{\fnsimhei})的知識\N是作為聲音來被認知的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到的是媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小開始就被無意識灌輸的各種知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現今的世界形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於島內部的{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及與敵人戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的人就算「畢業」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦知道 就無法回到平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要選擇和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚為什麼沒有離開島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親所設立的拯救島的L計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對父親的事情一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親一定想讓我參加這個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會唸著{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 你還什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就一直都明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒跟你出去 爸爸就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵前辈...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 普库
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业去向决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假结束以后 离开岛和大人们一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真将陵前辈很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于工作什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的话 羽佐间也一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我离开了 这句话一定要记着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要選擇和父親相同的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您成全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下終於可以報答給我容身之處的人們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业去向决定了 来打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了参加父亲的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才和校长已经谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 会直接和敌人战斗阿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前多少一样的计划我也听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果谁都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也... 那为什么你也要参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会藏在海里面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算就一直闭口不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去 不要再接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 選拔成員聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠自主催眠學習
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協同線路產生數值高的最適合者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天起負責各位訓練的日野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出作戰的人可隨時向我提出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始說明{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在敵人正逐漸察覺此島的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃正是為了避免之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即指{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的左翼 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其從島上分離開 成為{\fnArial}L Boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}能夠在超越敵人探知能力的深海中前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到島的防禦圈外上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引敵人 按既定航線繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為期兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓其誤以為{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}就是龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須持續迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}是自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己身在何處也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將是極其嚴苛的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出的人請提出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼立即開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第一大特徵 即無需操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵從催眠學習獲得的知識 和{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受精神的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是訓練用的虛擬現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.83,0:24:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.31,0:24:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跑 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.15,0:24:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸毫無困難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.77,0:24:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二大特徵 即各機內置系統間的交叉({\fnArial}Crossing{\fnsimhei})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:24:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共享思考 防止被敵人讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.90,0:25:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接受同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.61,0:25:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.22,0:25:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 請換其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是他 你馬上就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.08,0:25:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.07,0:25:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.11,0:25:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 你害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.59,0:25:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是僚的感覺？你在享受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上這個 我也能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制時間到 請離開駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.05,0:25:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第三大特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即駕駛員會被同化現象所侵擾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.38,0:25:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐次數越多 肉體越容易發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.08,0:25:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最壞情況下可能危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.84,0:25:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退出吧 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.49,0:26:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了爸爸一定要讓計劃成功
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.98,0:26:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是一開始就不想活著回去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.26,0:26:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如退出算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.54,0:26:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選拔成員共8人 無人退出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.39,0:26:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}共4架 每架由兩人交替駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次戰鬥時間15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.47,0:26:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人交替 各戰鬥450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷重複的戰鬥訓練 以及敵人的確認
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.86,0:26:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矽狀生命體 － {\fnArial}Festum {\fnsimhei}即敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.71,0:26:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有統一的思考 能適應任何環境
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.06,0:26:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但未曾在海中發現過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.87,0:26:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測是其若與海中結晶物同化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會成為不規則塊狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是「畢業」的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而對我來說 還有一項重要的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.13,0:27:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 普庫 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.52,0:27:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我給的 它從不吃任何食物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定察覺到會被丟下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶狗一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.31,0:27:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為飼主 要負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.49,0:27:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條狗是從前媽媽帶回來 讓我當成朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.74,0:27:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法去上學時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.56,0:27:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有它在身邊 我就不會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.59,0:27:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.29,0:27:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知有毒還去吃的對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.33,0:27:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.15,0:27:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.03,0:28:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.27,0:28:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖等著學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.50,0:28:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為獎勵 學長們的慰問品分你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.36,0:28:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.43,0:28:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後計劃完畢之前 應該趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們沒事 就能來迎接我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.18,0:28:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長 它好像肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.80,0:28:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.52,0:28:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這是隨身物品 可能有點重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.04,0:28:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.84,0:28:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.79,0:28:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我會把它當成學長好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.67,0:28:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.76,0:28:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 完成最後一項準備時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.36,0:28:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何想起了祐未的話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就覺得回不去的人 應該退出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.95,0:29:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 多半祐未是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.79,0:29:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝鏡面 維持{\fnArial}ROM{\fnsimhei}模式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.86,0:29:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 全部隔離壁以緊急模式封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全隔離壁封鎖確認
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟注水閥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.18,0:29:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 確認注水
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.64,0:29:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}艦橋呼叫{\fnArial}CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.88,0:29:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序鏈接無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.69,0:29:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注水完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.82,0:29:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat {\fnsimhei}出發準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.78,0:29:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域分離準備 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分離
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.91,0:29:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}控制程序開始運行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.73,0:29:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駛向波盾圈外
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.73,0:29:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後再會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.45,0:29:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝他們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.78,0:29:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二步驟啟動 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.91,0:29:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.54,0:30:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離計劃結束的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.68,0:30:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月2號 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.96,0:30:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即{\fnArial}Left {\fnsimhei}左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.35,0:30:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也含有離去的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.37,0:30:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如這個詞所說 我們離開了島
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.12,0:30:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發後第3天 我們的小島上浮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.77,0:30:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起 這裡就是龍宮島了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.32,0:30:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人實體化 是{\fnArial}Sphinx {\fnsimhei}型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.55,0:30:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以普通武器牽制 {\fnArial}Fafner {\fnsimhei}準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}能量傳輸線連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.76,0:30:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}7至8號
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.23,0:30:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Brunhild{\fnsimhei}系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.67,0:30:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}數據線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.62,0:30:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}搭乘輸入優先
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.68,0:30:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}速度控制
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.81,0:30:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}負極數據輸入中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.06,0:30:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}誤差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.84,0:30:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}傳感器開放
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.84,0:30:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}各機正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.17,0:30:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}封鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.69,0:30:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Niebelungen{\fnsimhei}系統開啟確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.45,0:30:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統接續完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.79,0:30:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}接續桿連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}艙門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.33,0:30:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}啟動升降架接續
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.09,0:30:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}上升
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.19,0:31:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}潮流數據 環境數據及氣象數據輸入完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.15,0:31:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到的敵人 超乎想像的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.74,0:31:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.78,0:31:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.69,0:32:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打倒敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.33,0:32:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次打倒敵人 大家深受鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.95,0:32:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試圖用興奮壓抑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.51,0:32:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有歸路了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.71,0:32:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 为什么我的饭你会吃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.47,0:32:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是被抛弃后一个人呢 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.35,0:32:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里曾是fafner的启动事件失败后 消灭后产生的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:33:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.82,0:33:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走错的话 就会葬身海里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.20,0:33:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也要做么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.55,0:33:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵前辈的事情想起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.32,0:33:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种的事 害怕什么的早就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.79,0:33:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想像的小
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.59,0:33:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒有內置{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.38,0:33:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.87,0:33:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.87,0:33:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markeins {\fnsimhei}終止啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.12,0:33:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}eins:{\fnsimhei}德語「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.80,0:33:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然對與{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化來說 是致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.56,0:33:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次 請讓我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.15,0:33:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.25,0:33:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.63,0:34:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員喪失意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.89,0:34:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3號機的駕駛員來這邊 交換
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.98,0:34:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩天一次 敵人不斷來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.21,0:34:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後有人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.67,0:34:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6次戰鬥時 那件事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.27,0:34:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是乘坐{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.24,0:34:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的肉體越會結晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.67,0:34:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第8次戰鬥時 又有一人倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.60,0:34:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.12,0:35:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是敵人 而是本應是武器的{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.82,0:35:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.63,0:35:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該把戰鬥時間從15分鐘縮短為10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.16,0:35:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣出擊次數就會增大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.72,0:35:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊時 牽制敵人的彈藥不足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.38,0:35:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反需要增加戰鬥時間
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.76,0:35:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.19,0:35:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.39,0:35:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從父親口中聽說過這個計劃的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.81,0:35:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.10,0:35:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃結束時的逃生方法是什麼 連我也未被告知
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.96,0:35:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便沒有逃生方法 我也早有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父親他 絕不會把我們當成犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父親並不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.29,0:35:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能提出這麼快就無法戰鬥的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.72,0:35:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該縮短戰鬥時間到10分鐘 減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.98,0:36:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與根據現狀的判斷相比 你更相信計劃立案者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.17,0:36:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父親自己也打算參加
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他想活著回島
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.59,0:36:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說重病纏身時日無多的人還打算生還嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.24,0:36:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.92,0:36:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時起 我就變得如此相信
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.86,0:36:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.43,0:36:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得 如果自己病情嚴重惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.47,0:36:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會比現在更想活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.96,0:36:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人在放哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.47,0:36:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.71,0:36:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.22,0:36:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.02,0:36:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.45,0:36:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太擔心的話 你又要發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.14,0:36:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候被人提起自己的身體 有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.98,0:36:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天謝謝你 替我父親辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.35,0:36:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.39,0:37:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是…對不起 你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.52,0:37:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為無法活著回去也無所謂的 是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.97,0:37:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你一直想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.14,0:37:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你和爸爸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯有你 我不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.43,0:37:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快到會議室來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.32,0:37:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.49,0:37:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封閉的區域自動開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.06,0:37:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給我們的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人會讀取我們的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判斷武器的能力而進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.92,0:37:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要騙過敵人先得騙過自己 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.57,0:37:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在一定時期後 就會提供一些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.71,0:38:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最後打開的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是逃生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.70,0:38:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 勿庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.22,0:38:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸果然了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要的一定是生存之地 而不是葬身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.62,0:38:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.82,0:38:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員另選其他人擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.47,0:38:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來操縱{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.61,0:38:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我不親臨陣前 反而把同伴送去戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這比較適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.12,0:38:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親認為這次計劃能有多少人生還
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.77,0:38:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒提出的生存率極低
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.82,0:38:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您依然批准了計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.15,0:38:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要我做同樣的事 為了保護島而付出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.88,0:38:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生駒想盡力生存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.99,0:39:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我批准了計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我堅信他們能夠全部生還
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.37,0:39:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在殘酷的境遇中掙扎求生者的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.74,0:39:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠背負嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.38,0:39:23.08,pic2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(473,201)}（活下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.39,0:39:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥越來越激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.66,0:39:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.71,0:40:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.07,0:40:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.13,0:40:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅有的4架{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}中 有一架喪失了機能
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.49,0:40:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的數量再次減少
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.68,0:40:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚能戰鬥的人身上 也出現了同化現象的早期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:32.51,pic3,NTP,0,0,0,,（希望早日結束）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.83,0:40:33.51,pic4,NTP,0,0,0,,（快點！快點！快點！我想回家！）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.69,0:40:34.41,pic5,NTP,0,0,0,,（爸爸 媽媽）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.55,0:40:35.18,pic6,NTP,0,0,0,,（我們在這裡）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.80,0:40:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 終於駕駛員中也開始出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.60,0:40:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸弘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.53,0:41:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是同化現象的末期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.78,0:41:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴們 一個接一個 在我們眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.49,0:41:19.95,pic7,NTP,0,0,0,,（反正大家最後都要死）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.12,0:41:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 為什麼寫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.88,0:41:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.90,0:41:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.82,0:41:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再逼他了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.89,0:41:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人的心中都充滿了恐懼 憤怒和悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.63,0:41:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下兩周
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.38,0:41:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我們再度失去了{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.32,0:42:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象的早期症狀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.57,0:42:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.81,0:42:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧這個 才不會被其他人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.55,0:42:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在第三次啟動時成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.88,0:42:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣身體就出現異變 真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.83,0:42:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長他們還要更加辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.25,0:42:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一派和平
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.02,0:42:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想把學長們的事告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.06,0:42:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會讓學長們的戰鬥變得毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人做出犧牲 卻只有我們待在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.21,0:42:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.40,0:42:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能祈求這是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.29,0:42:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說皆城已經決定操縱系統了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.13,0:42:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.51,0:42:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倖存下來的有兩架{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.65,0:42:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3名駕駛員和8位成人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.46,0:43:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.71,0:43:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡竟然有通道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.90,0:43:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是逃生方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.26,0:43:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.19,0:43:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.13,0:43:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.06,0:43:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 那艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠搭乘40人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.81,0:43:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸認為所有人都能生還
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.96,0:43:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.44,0:43:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經活到現在了 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.96,0:43:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第9至第17區域注水開始
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.68,0:43:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第1第2第3隔離壁開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.11,0:43:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}逃生程序確認
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.09,0:43:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想與{\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei}同歸於盡 銷毀這個島嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.21,0:43:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.67,0:43:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.96,0:44:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放還有5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.99,0:44:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.95,0:44:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.90,0:44:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.77,0:44:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.64,0:44:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦圈內有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.55,0:44:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潛水艇和{\fnArial}Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.40,0:44:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備出擊 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.61,0:44:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner·Markzwei {\fnsimhei}出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.15,0:44:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}zwei:{\fnsimhei}德語「2」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.13,0:44:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間正面出現{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短魚雷及導彈戰準備
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.09,0:44:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,252度也出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.54,0:44:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.53,0:45:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.34,0:45:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後方約20公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.50,0:45:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.49,0:45:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們幾時能下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.53,0:45:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛水艇消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.93,0:45:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島應該在這個方向 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.23,0:45:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.21,0:45:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經知道龍宮島在這前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.22,0:45:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.88,0:45:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能百分之百確定 就不能這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.87,0:45:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.24,0:45:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去 回島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.62,0:45:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況已經變了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.08,0:45:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能讓大家的戰鬥失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.77,0:45:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 在有人來迎接我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.82,0:45:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fnsimhei}開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.19,0:45:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠離島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 停住{\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.60,0:46:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能發生了最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.21,0:46:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.70,0:46:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓整座島置身險境 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.60,0:46:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}停止前進
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.37,0:46:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機 {\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.99,0:46:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況變了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.20,0:46:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 不是要去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.69,0:46:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定{\fnArial}Markzwei{\fnsimhei}的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.46,0:46:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你讓我去 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城 聽得見吧 為什麼不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.93,0:46:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.07,0:46:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.46,0:46:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}CDC {\fnsimhei}那邊是有著實戰經驗的機體和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.83,0:46:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能回收那些數據
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.68,0:47:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的戰力將大幅提升
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.35,0:47:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也更能抵抗敵人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.24,0:47:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲得與敵人戰鬥力量的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.27,0:47:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算眼睜睜地錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.36,0:47:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}是做什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.58,0:47:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.82,0:47:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能讓{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}離開防禦圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.71,0:47:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.51,0:47:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}重整機體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.17,0:47:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後全力追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.13,0:47:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.78,0:47:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計測目標週邊所有振動
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.11,0:47:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能得到答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.29,0:47:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流的數據收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.50,0:47:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這裡運氣好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.54,0:47:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少殘骸能回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.41,0:47:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.77,0:47:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.29,0:48:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 制止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.26,0:48:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.41,0:48:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.20,0:48:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我一直喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.99,0:48:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 從很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.94,0:48:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.89,0:48:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時 已經超越了那種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.16,0:48:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.22,0:48:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.33,0:48:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.89,0:48:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.25,0:48:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸會稱讚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.90,0:49:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？下在海底？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.96,0:49:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.96,0:49:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}海雪︰海底浮游生物組成的絮狀物，看起來像雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.87,0:49:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在稱讚我們呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.93,0:49:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.60,0:49:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在陪在我身邊的是你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.63,0:49:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.24,0:49:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.09,0:49:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.53,0:49:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像還有更多更深的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.66,0:49:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你陪在身邊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.60,0:50:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.06,0:50:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.76,0:50:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了嗎 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.29,0:50:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.99,0:50:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.62,0:50:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你們以前從未到過海中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.76,0:50:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由於無法代謝而結晶化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.74,0:51:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代謝…就是使身體重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.48,0:51:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也掌握了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.39,0:51:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 才擁有了生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.43,0:51:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.60,0:51:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認信源地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.32,0:51:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判斷為海底有人啟動了{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.17,0:51:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.97,0:51:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心機體被敵人同化
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.82,0:51:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明海底也存在{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.85,0:51:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給我們的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.07,0:51:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Markzwei 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.67,0:51:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡已經 沒有任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.09,0:52:04.05,pic8,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,276)\fad(2000,2000)}四\N個\N月\N後
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.00,0:52:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是第一波盾的潮流感應器探查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著珍貴的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.99,0:52:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.08,0:52:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 分析了潮流後才啟動的{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.43,0:52:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是保持鎮靜直到最後的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.95,0:52:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰駕駛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.46,0:52:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據調查 似乎只留下了音頻記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.78,0:52:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 普庫 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.32,0:52:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.37,0:52:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.40,0:53:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.29,0:53:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.20,0:53:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 待在這裡的是將陵學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.84,0:53:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是陪伴祐未學姐直到最後的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.84,0:54:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起 一定是去了將陵學長身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.47,0:54:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了 想把它送回龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.27,0:54:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的反應顯示著徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.87,0:54:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計很快將輪到{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}迎擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.93,0:54:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平僅僅維持了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.40,0:54:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長他們的戰鬥 只有這點意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.87,0:54:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直享受著別人贏來並讓給的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.77,0:54:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那和平只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.06,0:54:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會感謝其價值
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.38,0:54:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.42,0:54:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待與你並肩作戰的時刻到來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.03,0:55:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我們繼承了和平與戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.92,0:55:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想要活下去的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.28,0:55:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及在前線戰鬥者的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.52,0:55:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能否全部承受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.98,0:55:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不斷重複問著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.01,0:55:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案 就在今後的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.59,0:52:28.12,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どれくらい時間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.90,0:52:32.78,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心は繋がるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.02,0:52:39.56,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか寂しげな笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.92,0:52:44.02,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,癒せたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.64,0:52:52.05,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,近すぎて気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.86,0:52:57.21,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,一番大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.82,0:53:03.59,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,傍に居てくれるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.90,0:53:09.26,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,幸せを感じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.46,0:53:12.34,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しみの夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.41,0:53:15.34,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びの朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.41,0:53:21.37,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしを見守ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.88,0:53:27.53,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ一言「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.87,0:53:32.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,伝えられないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.35,0:53:36.26,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.39,0:53:39.22,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.43,0:53:44.84,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.94,0:53:51.84,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.08,0:54:01.04,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.59,0:54:16.05,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,静けさにふと窓の外
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.91,0:54:20.82,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,雪が舞い降りている
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.91,0:54:27.20,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,真白に染まる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.96,0:54:33.18,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの音に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.46,0:54:36.26,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.40,0:54:39.33,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.50,0:54:44.85,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.94,0:54:51.81,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.20,0:55:02.37,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.59,0:52:28.12,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要經過多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.90,0:52:32.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,心才能相映
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.02,0:52:39.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,些許寂寞的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.92,0:52:44.02,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,多想將其治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.64,0:52:52.05,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,太過靠近而未曾察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.86,0:52:57.21,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.82,0:53:03.59,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,只是陪在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.90,0:53:09.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.46,0:53:12.34,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.41,0:53:15.34,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.41,0:53:21.37,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,都為我守候
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.88,0:53:27.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,連一句感謝的話語
