Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.91,0:54:20.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,飄起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.91,0:54:27.20,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,在純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.96,0:54:33.18,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,依偎著你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.46,0:54:36.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.40,0:54:39.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.50,0:54:44.85,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,如今在你懷中
